{"tid":819518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知行合一的真英雄，美國《我的英雄學院》粉絲在Starbucks救出被襲擊女子","createTime":"2018-09-15T00:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T09:15:24.000Z","uid":1735,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eb648c327482d58844d21b4b3be37369abed7ff0","tid":819518,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"「要成為英雄」這句說話可能很多人在自己童年時代會說，但是真的能夠做到像英雄一樣在危難時刻挺身而出幫助他人的就是少之又少<br />\n最近美國加州的一位27歲《我的英雄學院》粉絲就做到知行合一，在現實生活中救助一位被襲擊的女性，不顧個人安危與襲擊者搏鬥為女性逃走贏得時間，而他本人也因此多處受傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/084046_63e22db89a3645de0fbd5b075181d2d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F084046_63e22db89a3645de0fbd5b075181d2d5.png&h=f871daf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在美國加州貝克斯菲爾德高速公路旁一間Starbucks中，一名男子因為家暴糾紛持械襲擊一名女子<br />\n當地27歲的音樂家Blaine Hodge見義勇為挺身而出與施襲的男性進行搏鬥，救出了這位女子，Blaine Hodge多處受傷與女子一起被送到醫院，目前兩人並無生命危險<br />\nBlaine Hodge是《我的英雄學院》粉絲，其英勇事蹟經媒體廣泛傳播後，美國的動畫粉絲們尤其是《我的英雄學院》粉絲們紛紛轉發關於Blaine Hodge的相關報導，連美國的萬代南夢宮娛樂官推也轉發相關報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/084116_fe027749d4990f9981d577c344e2bc2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F084116_fe027749d4990f9981d577c344e2bc2d.png&h=d4621530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件發生後還有人為Blaine Hodge開設眾籌籌集治療款項，原本預定的眾籌目標是9000美元，現在已經眾籌超過23000美元<br />\n有粉絲仿照歐爾麥特的造型繪製了Blaine Hodge的形象，剛巧Blaine Hodge在本月推出了自己的音樂專輯《The Mind of a Hero》 ，Blaine Hodge可以說是一位貨真價實的歐爾麥特One For All 精神繼承者<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/62233/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F62233%2F&d=SJef7YEcbR%2BCtWK2P4T1cqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=fe6591ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/62233/</a>"},{"pid":"8f48310ceffc7b66a9eb17c9a87fc3549a155058","tid":819518,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T00:43:42.000Z","msg":"真英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？定係炒作？"},{"pid":"88cdce1ca21ff38b6f07a5cb180a7a184fcb394b","tid":819518,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T01:06:59.000Z","msg":"張圖好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，比著香港人實走夾唔抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f3da8853c69d9c5fa257c5c3c54a3a69f1a8ff","tid":819518,"uid":181061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f48310ceffc7b66a9eb17c9a87fc3549a155058","tid":819518,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T00:43:42.000Z","msg":"真英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？定係炒作？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"係又點唔係又點"},{"pid":"250dbec34566f65840c0e4bc9087fd9016124154","tid":819518,"uid":146707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T01:19:54.000Z","msg":"如果喺香港會比人屌"},{"pid":"f4565d846f330122ff8ea307852ad76641440c49","tid":819518,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T01:20:58.000Z","msg":"黑人👎"},{"pid":"cc9c2d7d79958dba531106cc0e555b8c0d82f683","tid":819518,"uid":41076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"88cdce1ca21ff38b6f07a5cb180a7a184fcb394b","tid":819518,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T01:06:59.000Z","msg":"張圖好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，比著香港人實走夾唔抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"梗走<br />\n喺香港噉做會畀警犬告埋一份<br />\n然後班成日話香港冇英雄嘅人就一齊恥笑佢"},{"pid":"1d638673b021b8b6551fef68337a957f45dc5f50","tid":819518,"uid":151071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T01:23:27.000Z","msg":"好彩條友無槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm